#. <section class="sutta" id="an3.5"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an3.5:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 3"
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 3"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "an3.5:0.2"
msgid "1. Bālavagga"
msgstr "1. Fools"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "an3.5:0.3"
msgid "5. Ayonisosutta"
msgstr "5. Improper"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "an3.5:1.1"
msgid "“Tīhi, bhikkhave, dhammehi samannāgato bālo veditabbo."
msgstr "“A fool is known by three things."

msgctxt "an3.5:1.2"
msgid "Katamehi tīhi?"
msgstr "What three?"

# Upagata in this sense i take as “staying close” i.e. “sticking to the point”, i.e. relevant.
msgctxt "an3.5:1.3"
msgid ""
"Ayoniso pañhaṃ kattā hoti, ayoniso pañhaṃ vissajjetā hoti, parassa kho pana "
"yoniso pañhaṃ vissajjitaṃ parimaṇḍalehi padabyañjanehi siliṭṭhehi upagatehi "
"nābbhanumoditā hoti."
msgstr ""
"They ask a question improperly. They answer a question improperly. And when "
"someone else answers a question properly—with well-rounded, coherent, and "
"relevant words and phrases—they disagree with it."

msgctxt "an3.5:1.4"
msgid "Imehi kho, bhikkhave, tīhi dhammehi samannāgato bālo veditabbo."
msgstr "These are the three things by which a fool is known."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "an3.5:2.1"
msgid "Tīhi, bhikkhave, dhammehi samannāgato paṇḍito veditabbo."
msgstr "An astute person is known by three things."

msgctxt "an3.5:2.2"
msgid "Katamehi tīhi?"
msgstr "What three?"

msgctxt "an3.5:2.3"
msgid ""
"Yoniso pañhaṃ kattā hoti, yoniso pañhaṃ vissajjetā hoti, parassa kho pana "
"yoniso pañhaṃ vissajjitaṃ parimaṇḍalehi padabyañjanehi siliṭṭhehi upagatehi "
"abbhanumoditā hoti."
msgstr ""
"They ask a question properly. They answer a question properly. And when "
"someone else answers a question properly—with well-rounded, coherent, and "
"relevant words and phrases—they agree with it."

msgctxt "an3.5:2.4"
msgid "Imehi kho, bhikkhave, tīhi dhammehi samannāgato paṇḍito veditabbo."
msgstr "These are the three things by which an astute person is known."

msgctxt "an3.5:2.5"
msgid "Tasmātiha … pe …."
msgstr "So you should train …”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an3.5:2.6"
msgid "Pañcamaṃ."
msgstr ""
